"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"*he ‘tipping point’ for a currency seems to be when society realizes en masse why prices are really going up — namely, that the denominator of a price (the currency) is going down in value. All prices are just ratios, expressed as the value of the good (numerator) in terms of the currency (denominator).”*\\n\\n[Cointelegraph](https://cointelegraph.com/news/here-are-the-top-10-books-blockchain-thought-leaders-recommend-in-2020)\\n\\n**Biography:**\\n\\nA Wall Street veteran, Caitlin Long first came across Bitcoin in 2012 in economics circles at the Austrian School. She fully immersed herself in 2013 when an article on how to buy and store Bitcoin hit her inbox. With a passion for “honest ledgers” and the goal to make securities markets fairer by issuing and trading securities on a blockchain, Long was chairwoman and president of the blockchain startup Symbiont until 2018. \",\"timestamp\":1639030191,\"title\":\"The ‘tipping point’ for a currency seems\"},\"digest\":\"-QGyvHYelSkM5ftYw015yCSodz5PGVzfnB6qTHHk96o\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xf3422a2D7f7810128D6F94A176cAdcf6Daf15D59\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"3O9eAsD_A6vPjd8oRDZZyNbolQAANcNX_pvhmcSRlzA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"gVumb1TuOSeP1eXF4qZC9d6eSFsNp_BWmgQKAPDreoE\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"x9GNJeuADBNslI9WIzwW1ZfROZZlw8JFHBYd43IAGOhRjU8bFJ9wM8lBuCGTkuBvlcmmFzxYbF8gWt21q-lW6Q\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x9a75b66e38222504dcbc9b7577cfd625947f1ec251a60e62fd4e80019aa6ca973bcfd5885fad03e4613e68f4a2de4fe67ace2e4df9d2f1e8780c06d28f8a06af1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"3O9eAsD_A6vPjd8oRDZZyNbolQAANcNX_pvhmcSRlzA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"gVumb1TuOSeP1eXF4qZC9d6eSFsNp_BWmgQKAPDreoE\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\